{"tid":1793570,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"今日我做野間酒樓有食客反枱，仲差D打交","createTime":"2019-12-22T13:16:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-22T13:34:32.000Z","uid":172668,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"a3f4f706ff57b9e6343c92cf6edd5b229db66db8","tid":1793570,"uid":172668,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-22T13:16:07.000Z","msg":"今日冬至，本身酒樓因為班防暴曱甴都無以前咁好生意<br />\n但係今日都叫無平時咁靜<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n做野都叫幾忙下<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n點知有張枱食客越講越嘈，見到有幾個後生仔女好激動<br />\n隔離啲廢老就&rdquo;拿&rdquo;住囗面，講嘢越嚟越大聲<br />\n基本上睇表情同陣容都知咩事㗎啦<br />\n肯定又係因為啲藍絲戇鳩言論<br />\n<br />\n本身以為冇乜嘢好快就會靜<br />\n畢竟都係冬至飯<br />\n咁啱我上道山東雞俾個客既時候<br />\n轟啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n個客夾無耐既雞髀跌咗落地下<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/treat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n跟住有個後生仔直接反枱跟住頭也不回<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n跟住全場人突然靜音5秒，連個廚房佬都沖出嚟睇咩事，我自己個口都擘大合唔埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n跟住嗰幾個廢老呆咗最少5分鐘，都無辦法，呢枱人都無得食，咁我就行上去問佢要唔要上埋個水果，打算快快趣趣趕走呢班廢老<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n跟住佢話唔使<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 仲好省返<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n喺邊間做就唔自爆啦<br />\n手足支持你<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nbtw 後尾防暴曱甴係附近包圍左我個商場<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n班客個個即刻飯都唔食埋單走人<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n而家我仲執緊枱 希望收工既時候班防暴曱甴已經死曬返狗屋<br />\n唔係唯有係公司瞓<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/sick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"93eed20dd977924912693d02750fa0860a1a0ff0","tid":1793570,"uid":172668,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-22T13:20:20.000Z","msg":"屌你老母你班防暴曱甴死未<br />\n日日係我公司出面埋伏搞事<br />\n而家我班客話驚左你班曱甴唔肯黎<br />\n香港警察正一社會敗類人渣<br />\n有破壞無建設"},{"pid":"d84dc20731eb6b5c9091ecb797929de774104bad","tid":1793570,"uid":15880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-22T13:22:34.000Z","msg":"鄧炳強: 冬至多後生女, 係咪捉幾個強姦都唔得先"},{"pid":"e39fb4f038105743227f1c48b53e02c6747b3198","tid":1793570,"uid":331949,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-22T13:22:39.000Z","msg":"反佢檯！"},{"pid":"497ec7ad235b6866bd494d3014e700121f345147","tid":1793570,"uid":119585,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-22T13:32:34.000Z","msg":"手足好撚型<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"36432a5e4f80a2a47182b6003baaa34d9bc6951f","tid":1793570,"uid":113241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-22T13:34:32.000Z","msg":"俄羅斯娃娃<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}